        "subject": "LU-14708 tests: improve recovery-small test_155",
        "message": "LU-14708 tests: improve recovery-small test_155\n\nThis test is failing intermittently in Janitor testing (though not\nin Autotest), but it is difficult to see why it fails.\n\nWrite the 'ls' output to temporary files and use 'diff' to compare\nthem, so that it is easier to see what the differences are, instead\nof just comparing the output strings and printing both of them in\nthe error message.\n\nIt appears it fails due to a previous subtest file changing:\n- -rw-r--r-- 1 root root     512 Mar  2 18:52 f131.recovery-small\n+ -rw-r--r-- 1 root root       0 Mar  2 18:52 f131.recovery-small\n\nFlush client before the test to avoid any issues with old files.\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial\nFixes: 71f8e5d650 (\"LU-14708 ptlrpc: skip unnecessary client eviction\")\nSigned-off-by: Andreas Dilger <adilger@thelustrecollective.com>\nChange-Id: I9483f1579a51267e12051682f379ba55473ebbe5\nReviewed-on: https://review.whamcloud.com/c/fs/lustre-release/+/64332\nTested-by: Maloo <maloo@whamcloud.com>\nReviewed-by: Jian Yu <yujian@whamcloud.com>\nReviewed-by: Oleg Drokin <green@whamcloud.com>\nTested-by: jenkins <devops@whamcloud.com>\nReviewed-by: Arshad Hussain <arshad.hussain@aeoncomputing.com>\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
  },
